;Notes :{{note|dvi_ok|DVI compatible}} HDMI signal can be converted to DVI by passive adapter. :{{note|dvi_no|DVI incompatible}} HDMI signal not convertible to DVI by passive adapter. Watch out for HDMI screens that require DVI signalling.
